Well, I guess you would all like to know about Eugene, the flower that lived in a flower pot but one morining Eugene woke and and he was in a boot instead of his beloved flower pot. Well, Eugene wasn't any old flower, he was a Juskaliverwatchi. Juskaliverwatchi flowers are really just any other stupid flower so that doesn't matter anyways. So, his name was Eugene. He lived in a flower pot. One day he rolled himself into town to find that he wasn't in town, he was in china. He has roleld himself into a hole. The hole was hand dug by little billy whoppersville. Little Billy Whoppersville was a very determined 1 year old and his parents one day told him to go dig a hole to china, so he did and they didn't belive him so they told him to come inside and watch some good old fashioned TV. SO, Little Billy Whoppersville did not get the chance to fill in his Hole To China and poor little Eugene just happened to be in the little flower pot that rolled into Little Billy Whoppersville's Hole To China. Well, when in China you must learn how to communicate so Eugene learned from other local  flowers who were very helpful. Then he met a caterpillar sitting on a mushroom and learned the vowels (in chinese of course). Then Eugene got hungry, as all flowers do, and took a bite out of the mushroom. Poor Eugene ate the wrong side and shrunk. But that was okay because Eugene was overweight anyways. So, after shrinking to average Juskaliverwatchi size, Eugene found his lighter self easier to roll around and rolled down a big chiense hill called mount everest. Eugene was then named the first flower to ever roll Mount everest but Eugene's mission was far from over. Eugene rolled to the part of down called BeJing. He the rolled out of that place because he almost got ran over by one of them damn bike riding chinese hooligans. He rolled into a quieter part of china and by then it was very late and Eugene the Juskaliverwatchi flower decided to stay under a nice picnic table for that night. During the night a starving atrist named Kwok Fu Yu decided to look under his picnic table and found Eugene. He knew he should not wake up Eugene or he might revolt and roll away. So, knowing this Kwok Fu Yu quietly found a big bright pink plastic boot and transplanted Eugene into that. When Eugene woke up he decided to go rolling but couldn't flip over and when he did, it wouldn't move. Then Eugene look down and said "Shit, I've been transplanted into a big bright pink plastic boot overnight by a starving artist named Kwok Fu Yu who came out in the middle of the night and knew not to wake me or I might revolt and roll away!" THE END
